      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "&amp;gt; ***For Registration as a Building/ Construction Worker:***\n\n\n  - The applicant should be a Building/ Construction Worker (Unorganised Worker).\n  - The applicant should be a minimum of 18 years of age.\n  - The applicant should have engaged in building and construction work for at least 90 days in a given year.\n\n&amp;gt; **For the Application of the Welfare Scheme:**\n\n\n  - The beneficiary should be a nominee of a deceased registered construction worker Under the Building and Other Construction Workers Welfare Board of Karnataka.\n\n",
